{"tid":2139270,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞總薪金冠絕全歐！喊出了衝擊歐聯冠軍口號","createTime":"2020-08-04T07:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T21:45:59.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f26964bdb98e0d4b2aef703968242f545c4fd92e","tid":2139270,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"歐聯的比賽即將開始，巴塞方面喊出了衝擊冠軍的口號，不過傷病和停賽給巴塞帶來了難題，施迪安的球隊可以用的一隊球員人數十分有限。<br />\n<br />\n  巴塞是歐洲球員薪金總額最高的球隊，一隊球員的年薪相加達到了3.92億歐元。其他豪門中，曼聯球員薪金總額3.68億歐，曼城3.26億歐，皇馬2.83億歐。<br />\n<br />\n  不過巴塞在歐聯上的用人如今卻捉襟見肘。球會在歐聯中註冊了31名球員，其中13人是二隊編製，18名一隊球員中，有2人停賽（布斯基斯和維達爾），還有1人受傷（安迪堤）。<br />\n<br />\n  鋒線上，比夫韋治（Martin Braithwaite）沒有歐聯參賽資格，基沙文（Antoine Griezmann）和迪比利（Ousmane Dembele）雖然復出，但明顯缺乏節奏，迪比利更是已經8個多月沒上場。中場現在只能用3名一隊球員（迪莊&nbsp;Frenkie de Jong、拿傑迪錫&nbsp;Ivan Rakitic&nbsp;和羅拔圖&nbsp;Sergi Roberto），羅拔圖主要還是踢右閘。加上二隊的佩治（Riqui Puig）也才4人。而美路（Arthur&nbsp;Melo）至今拒絕歸隊。<br />\n<br />\n  後防線情況也不妙，唯一沒有傷病的是比基（Gerard Pique），安迪堤（Samuel Umtiti）和阿勞霍（Ronald Araujo）都有傷，朗格勒（Clement Lenglet）最近也一直在養傷。最近，巴塞挑選了多名二隊球員跟隨一隊訓練，其中有多人將進入比賽大名單，但歐聯這樣重要的比賽，巴塞教練施迪安顯然不敢對他們委以重任。<br />\n<br />\n  支付著歐洲最高的薪金，球隊陣容到了關鍵時刻卻缺兵少將，巴塞的球隊規劃和競技管理真的有很大問題"},{"pid":"78a166102217c121e040af51d0c92c7d42ea49d7","tid":2139270,"uid":233327,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6b43b631c248082db7e0e0bb9a369da224a1e4","tid":2139270,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"又黑二弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3c49adb57726ae58659ea67a4278b037bddb12","tid":2139270,"uid":23672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"連續幾年世界級買人＋賣走晒青訓＋成班高薪老人<br />\n仲有歐聯踢都執到啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99164cf2351d5b2d90b9ddf0673e54ee7f6d755","tid":2139270,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca3c49adb57726ae58659ea67a4278b037bddb12","tid":2139270,"uid":23672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"連續幾年世界級買人＋賣走晒青訓＋成班高薪老人<br />\n仲有歐聯踢都執到啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:36:05.000Z","msg":"年年有過億球星加盟，目標高d得唔得"},{"pid":"750cbffab98fe6e8feddf93784b6812f6621809f","tid":2139270,"uid":134801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"踢條撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過主啦"},{"pid":"828ff390f086f54f06fcfde56b935f10e95f64cf","tid":2139270,"uid":58242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78a166102217c121e040af51d0c92c7d42ea49d7","tid":2139270,"uid":233327,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b5d820375eb98536c0efe3dd7384792ea15fe6","tid":2139270,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:45:59.000Z","msg":"下年再衝"}]}